OL,3,CCouncil's fury at 'unacceptable'
OL,4,Cdelays to flood-hit residents
OL,6,FA council has criticised the
OL,7,F"unacceptable" lack of response from
OL,8,Fthe management company and owner of an
OL,9,Fapartment building flooded on New
OL,10,FYear's Day - leaving many residents in
OL,11,F"complete crisis".
OL,13,FResidents living in Meadow Mill in
OL,14,FStockport, Greater Manchester, remain
OL,15,Fwithout electricity, heating, and
OL,16,Fwater, more than a week after they
OL,17,Fwere evacuated from the building.
