OL,3,CCouncil's fury at 'unacceptable'
OL,4,Cdelays to flood-hit residents
OL,6,FMore than 400 people had to be
OL,7,Fevacuated from the converted mill on
OL,8,FNew Year's Day after the building's
OL,9,Fcar park and lower floors were
OL,10,Fflooded, cutting off water and power
OL,11,Fsupplies and leaving residents
OL,12,Fstranded.
OL,14,FThe councillors claim people living in
OL,15,Fthe apartments are struggling without
OL,16,Fclear guidance on insurance claims or
OL,17,Ftemporary accommodation, with some
OL,18,Fforced to pay for hotel accommodation
OL,19,F"up front".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
