OL,3,CCouncil's fury at 'unacceptable'
OL,4,Cdelays to flood-hit residents
OL,6,FHowever, they added that "desperation
OL,7,Fis growing" with many residents now
OL,8,Freporting that financially they have
OL,9,Fto move back in to the building
OL,10,Fwithout electricity, water or
OL,11,Fappropriate safety measures in place
OL,12,Fto protect them.
OL,14,F"It is now over a week since the
OL,15,Fflood," the councillors said, "and
OL,16,Fmore delay and lack of certainty over
OL,17,Ftemporary
OL,19,Faccommodation arrangements will be of
OL,20,Fcold comfort to the residents, many of
OL,21,Fwhom are now in complete crisis.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
