OL,3,CCouncil's fury at 'unacceptable'
OL,4,Cdelays to flood-hit residents
OL,6,F"We would urge all parties to act
OL,7,Fswiftly, as they should have done from
OL,8,Fthe start, to provide the residents
OL,9,Faffected with the information and
OL,10,Fpractical assistance they need as a
OL,11,Fresult of having to leave their homes."
OL,13,FA CERT spokesperson said they have
OL,14,Fbeen communicating with flat owners
OL,15,Fand landlords "daily" since New Year's
OL,16,FDay and they aim to "have the power
OL,17,Fback on in communal landlord areas" by
OL,18,FMonday, 13 January.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
