OL,3,CCouncil's fury at 'unacceptable'
OL,4,Cdelays to flood-hit residents
OL,6,FIn a statement, CERT said: "We
OL,7,Funderstand that the uncertainty around
OL,8,Fwhen residents can return to their
OL,9,Fhomes, and whether they will be
OL,10,Freimbursed for their personal costs
OL,11,Fsince the event is very difficult and
OL,12,Fconfusing, and we are sympathetic to
OL,13,Ftheir position.
OL,15,F"Our communications have been issued
OL,16,Fdaily with the intention of keeping
OL,17,Fall parties informed of the most
OL,18,Frecent position."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
